<div class="prose-content max-w-3xl">

  <div class="bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded-lg p-5 mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-alert-urgent text-lg font-bold mb-2">Emergency? Call 999</h2>
    <p class="text-neutral-dark">If you or someone else is in immediate danger or has a life-threatening emergency, call <a href="tel:999" class="text-alert-urgent font-bold">999</a> or go to your nearest A&amp;E immediately.</p>
  </div>

  <h2>When we're closed — call NHS 24</h2>
  <p>When the surgery is closed, NHS 24 provides urgent medical advice and treatment.</p>
  <div class="bg-brand-light rounded-lg p-5 mb-6">
    <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-1"><a href="tel:111" class="no-underline text-brand-primary">111</a></p>
    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-mid">Free to call, 24 hours a day, 7 days a week<br>Also available online at <a href="https://www.nhsinform.scot/" rel="noopener noreferrer">NHS Inform Scotland</a></p>
  </div>

  <h2>Our opening hours</h2>
  <p>The surgery is open Monday to Friday, 08:00 to 18:00. We are closed on weekends and public holidays.</p>
  <p>On days when we are open, call us on <a href="tel:{{ site.phone | replace(' ', '') }}">{{ site.phone }}</a> from 08:00 for urgent same-day appointments.</p>

  <h2>Minor injuries</h2>
  <p>For cuts, burns, sprains, suspected fractures, or animal bites, a Minor Injuries Unit (MIU) can treat you — often without a long wait. Call NHS 111 to check your nearest open unit and get directions before travelling.</p>

  <h2>Other urgent services</h2>

  <h3>Dental emergencies</h3>
  <p>For urgent dental problems, please do not come to the health centre — we are unable to treat dental conditions. Call the <strong>Fife Dental Help Line</strong> for advice and to access emergency dental care.</p>
  <div class="bg-brand-light rounded-lg p-4 mb-4">
    <p class="font-bold text-brand-primary"><a href="tel:01592226555" class="no-underline text-brand-primary">01592 226 555</a></p>
    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-mid">Fife Dental Help Line — urgent dental advice and out-of-hours access</p>
  </div>

  <h3>Mental health crisis</h3>
  <p>If you are experiencing a mental health crisis, you can call NHS 24 on <a href="tel:111">111</a> and ask for the mental health team.</p>
  <p><strong>Breathing Space</strong> is a free, confidential Scottish helpline for anyone feeling low, anxious, or depressed:</p>
  <div class="bg-brand-light rounded-lg p-4 mb-4">
    <p class="font-bold text-brand-primary"><a href="tel:08008385587" class="no-underline text-brand-primary">0800 83 85 87</a></p>
    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-mid">Monday–Thursday: 6pm–2am &nbsp;|&nbsp; Friday 6pm–Monday 6am<br>Free to call from mobiles and landlines</p>
  </div>
  <p>The <strong>Samaritans</strong> are also available 24 hours a day, 7 days a week on <a href="tel:116123">116 123</a> (free, no caller ID needed).</p>

</div>
